!!!Emergency mode of action
The scale and urgency of what needs to be done to provide strong protection for the climate vulnerable is so great that it will not be deliverable in time if governments and societies don't go into emergency action mode.  Effective emergency action will depend on a massive mobilisation of communities and their economies.